rows.label: qst701504_msg0002
rows.name:
Strange. There shouldn't be no
one here. The inn is open.

rows.label: qst701504_msg0004
rows.name:
I'll go take a look.
Mirei-san, please wait here.

rows.label: qst701504_msg0005
rows.name:
This might be meddling, but...
there were shoe prints outside.
Could they be a clue?

rows.label: qst701504_msg0007
rows.name:
It's been decades since I've seen
my former husband. I was so nervous
I kept looking at my feet, fufu.

rows.label: qst701504_msg0008
rows.name:
I wonder what kind of face I
should make... Even at this age,
I still worry about such things.

rows.label: qst701504_msg0009
rows.name:
It's as if I've gone back
to that time. Even though
time doesn't go back...
